#	-mimetype mime
#
# putfile::status token
# putfile::ncode token
# putfile::ncodetotext ncode
# putfile::size token
# putfile::error token
#
# Callback interface:
#	-command:	PutCommand {token what msg}
#			what is "ok" or "error"
#	-progress:	PutProgress {token total current}
#			total is file size in bytes, and current is bytes so far

